### Node.js Basic Function Wrapper with Shim.wrap

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/documentation/function-wrapping.md

This JavaScript code demonstrates a basic wrapper using New Relic's Shim.wrap method in Node.js. It replaces the 'helloWorld' method of 'testObject' with a new function that logs a custom message, illustrating how to intercept and modify method behavior.

```javascript
// our wrappers will go here
// ...

shim.wrap(testObject, 'helloWorld', function wrapCreator(){
    return function wrappedHelloWorld(console) {
        console.log("I am the new method!");
    }
});
```

